  • Field Details

    • absoluteEncoder

      public final AbsoluteEncoderConfigAccessor absoluteEncoder
      Accessor for parameters relating to the absolute encoder. To configure these values, use AbsoluteEncoderConfig and call SparkBase.configure(SparkBaseConfig, SparkBase.ResetMode, SparkBase.PersistMode).

      NOTE: This uses calls that are blocking to retrieve parameters and should be used infrequently.
